{
  "3114380": {
    "name": "The HELL Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3114380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/275d77bfdba917aa3889243b8671b9ba.avif?t=1767862876\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras_big/275d77bfdba917aa3889243b8671b9ba.webp?t=1767862876 width=1560 height=159 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/9a54fa86f1c243501366cb467c7a7526.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/9a54fa86f1c243501366cb467c7a7526.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/9a54fa86f1c243501366cb467c7a7526.mp4?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为地狱总管，<strong>你的任务不仅是建造一座城市</strong>，更是要在罪恶主宰的领域中，将混乱化为秩序。在这里，<strong>每一个决定，每一个灵魂，都至关重要。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款城市建造游戏中，你将<strong>在这废墟上打造一座亡者之城，平衡有限资源，并控制来到狱界的灵魂们</strong>。面对源自七宗罪的挑战，与被坠入狱界并成为这领域的守卫，坠狱兽对峙。每个任务都深挖背景故事，考验你的战略智慧，而每一次失败，都是迈向复兴的基石。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次轮回，都是新的磨砺——过去的错误成为未来的力量，每一次尝试都让你离塑造不朽传奇更近一步。《大地狱》以沉浸式叙事与动态玩法挑战你，在这片土地上，每一座建筑都诉说着罪孽、苦难与救赎的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/a89a41b818c80611d6fbfb2f9b0c0467.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/a89a41b818c80611d6fbfb2f9b0c0467.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/ef65b0b3a8704c2f5c5e5dc93d2580fb.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1262 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的统治将跨越数个世纪</strong>，灵魂们源源不断地涌入狱界，皆来自人类最惨烈的灾难时刻——从古北欧神话中的严冬“芬布尔之冬”，到日本毁灭性的关东大地震，以及公元600至700年间至18世纪的各类浩劫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，你将体验七大沉浸式关卡，塑造你的狱界秩序：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>狂鲶震舞（关东，日本，1923年）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恶犬寡妇（喀拉喀托火山，印度尼西亚，1883年）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>万毒贪龙（墨西哥中部，南美州，1540年）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>四神之鹿 （斯堪的纳维亚，欧洲西北角，公元536年）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鳄神之吻 ( 古老埃及， 公元前1200年）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>巨蛇之梦 (古美索不达米亚，公元前3500年）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>颠倒乾坤 （__________)</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/39ed008195d90c3a69ee89aa5ce59709.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/39ed008195d90c3a69ee89aa5ce59709.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个任务都有独特的环境设定，并围绕七宗罪之一展开剧情，对应一位强大的坠狱兽。每张地图都带来截然不同的体验与挑战，确保每次任务都独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/f15ca5fd46684a0af1854572203bf648.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/f15ca5fd46684a0af1854572203bf648.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/6f683cad73934de0037a65fe1a50fbd3.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1269 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不同于传统城市建造游戏只关注人口增长</strong>，《大地狱》挑战你将这些灵魂转化为“奴民”——支撑亡者之城运转的关键劳力。灵魂从坠狱兽巨口喷涌而出，四散流窜，最终汇聚至一座耸立于亡者之城中的狱眼灵塔，邪恶的单眼无情凝视着每一个被诅咒的灵魂。它注视之下，灵魂将在痛苦中被审判，沦为奴民，成为你统治的无情齿轮。在这里，游荡的亡魂被逐一引导完成转化，成为地狱劳动力的脊梁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当灾难降临，大地震颤，屏幕剧烈晃动，让你沉浸在狱界的无尽威能之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在转化之前，所有灵魂都会被囚禁于一个特殊区域——“等不亭”。这里分为三个独特区域——火焰亭、冰霜亭与血液亭，它们各自影响着灵魂最终的形态。在此，每个灵魂都静候裁决，为你的转化流程增添更多深度与策略性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/dcaf207651f295935d94acaecdfd2502.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/dcaf207651f295935d94acaecdfd2502.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/dcaf207651f295935d94acaecdfd2502.mp4?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/2a9c5efdd63e541b5baefdc48859f7ef.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/2a9c5efdd63e541b5baefdc48859f7ef.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/2a9c5efdd63e541b5baefdc48859f7ef.mp4?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/513d9cd6e824ec4de1b1412277fbec2d.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/513d9cd6e824ec4de1b1412277fbec2d.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/513d9cd6e824ec4de1b1412277fbec2d.mp4?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/886b8e08008112ac5baa933aa04b0972.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1277 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >资源管理是打造繁荣亡者之城的关键。作为地狱总管，<strong>你必须好好运用四大核心资源——血液、残余、哭泪与恐惧</strong>，以维持城市运转并扩张你的亡者之城。这些资源由特定建筑生成，各具独特作用：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>血液</strong>：为城市提供能量，维持基础设施运作，确保一切正常运行。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>残余</strong>：建造与城市发展的关键原料。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>哭泪</strong>：用于探索“求签树”，解锁新科技与战略选项，提升城市能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恐惧</strong>：用于下令七宗罪之力，解锁新能力，助你掌控混乱局势。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/ac273ab1843482345b2148292fc7ddff.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/ac273ab1843482345b2148292fc7ddff.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高效管理这些资源至关重要，它不仅决定着亡者之城的建设与防御，还关系到你如何在坠狱兽之力的冲击下维持秩序，防止一切被摧毁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/16a89aa0535799cf7c46301ccf270f05.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/16a89aa0535799cf7c46301ccf270f05.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/16a89aa0535799cf7c46301ccf270f05.mp4?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，你可以<strong>实时监控资源流动</strong>——开采与搬运的资源将储存在仓库中，随时可用于建造与其他运营需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，灵魂分为三种不同的颜色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>蓝魂：</strong>沉稳顺从，满足城市的基本需求，耐心等待转化为奴民或警卫。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黄魂：</strong>焦躁不安，接近愤怒，随时准备进入转化流程，只需腾出足够奴屋才能化解。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>红魂：</strong>极端暴戾，愤怒达到顶点时，将化为破坏者——冷酷无情的存在，会掠夺资源并消灭你宝贵的单位。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/19eb93f623f5931d97526ebeb36e0e07.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/19eb93f623f5931d97526ebeb36e0e07.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当绝境来临时，你可以献祭现有单位，如奴民或警卫，以随机获取资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/cfe827e9115ef928e63172c441fc6fad.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/cfe827e9115ef928e63172c441fc6fad.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/cfe827e9115ef928e63172c441fc6fad.mp4?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/45394635fd53808972d98f8bc112b3a5.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1272 height=171 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的亡者之城永无宁日。神秘势力与无可预测的混乱时刻威胁着你的统治。为了抵御这些危机，你可以<strong>将奴民转化为专职警卫——他们将成为你的狱界警卫</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/5dc89aafdf0db0d1fd4f1b5c41d36d75.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/5dc89aafdf0db0d1fd4f1b5c41d36d75.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些警卫不仅能守护关键建筑，安抚狂躁灵魂，还能主动抵御突发威胁。想象你的普通灵魂化身迅捷而无情的守护者，在黑暗侵袭之际挺身而出，筑起抵御混乱的屏障。不断进化与调整防御策略，才能让你的城市在地狱永恒的混乱中屹立不倒，成为秩序与力量的堡垒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为应对城市的混乱，你可以将无业奴民转化为专职单位：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>守卫</strong>：驻守建筑，震慑盗取资源的浅渊者。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>安灵</strong>：安抚狂躁灵魂，降低内部骚乱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>猎魔</strong>：追捕并消灭威胁秩序的狂杀与偷窃。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/f4198db6813b4068f53ad116dab6ef5c.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/f4198db6813b4068f53ad116dab6ef5c.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/6397e8b09d18b5b91e22d53b46bd70bc.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1272 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在总府中下令七宗罪的强大力量，解锁你作为地狱总管的全部潜能</strong>。每种罪孽都赋予你强大的能力，深刻影响你的策略与亡者之城的命运。除此之外，利用求签树的神秘技能，全面强化城市运作，并探索及解锁关键升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/2863bd15ed2d79fcb0449d2e6e4bf49e.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/2863bd15ed2d79fcb0449d2e6e4bf49e.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/2863bd15ed2d79fcb0449d2e6e4bf49e.mp4?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能在混乱之中崛起，于诅咒烈焰中铸就不朽传奇？还是会被无尽的灵魂洪流与罪孽的黑暗诱惑吞噬？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/d773c7155a3e4f1016f5c52d367c72da.poster.avif?t=1767862876\" width=1170 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/d773c7155a3e4f1016f5c52d367c72da.webm?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114380/extras/d773c7155a3e4f1016f5c52d367c72da.mp4?t=1767862876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无数灵魂，坠狱兽逼近，禁忌已然浮现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大地狱，等待着你的灵魂。阿门。</p>",
